Is caused by the fact that ZRH has Platform UI (views, workbench) as binary and
text editor stuff in source, however all those things contribute their stuff via
org.eclipse.ui plugin.xml. You probably changed the name of the pref page class
which now no longer matches to what we have in binary (drop I20030129).
